translate ru ArrivingInAlGahaem_102c519d:
    # "As they continued further into the castle, Sarah began to notice just how many different peoples were here."
    ""

translate ru ArrivingInAlGahaem_220165af:
    # "In Rosanna, most everyone was from Rosanna, but here, all the people's from all the corners of the world seemed to mingle in one large hive."
