translate ru ArrivingInAlGahaem_3ee607f6:
    # "The room stretched so far in each direction, that it almost seemed hard to see the other side."
    ""

translate ru ArrivingInAlGahaem_d2adae89:
    # "The floor was filled with people sitting in circles, discussing, bartering, debating."
    ""

translate ru ArrivingInAlGahaem_fe19fcc9:
    # "In this room, her nakedness was more novel and more observed, and Sarah felt herself grow more conscious of it."
